Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:07.24,CR_DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,I spent all night thinking about my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:09.78,CR_DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,for playing in this band now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:14.95,CR_Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,We're Kessoku Band.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:21.75,CR_Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,We're going to play our song, \N"Guitar, Solitude, and the Blue Planet"!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:26.67,CR_DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,I do still want to become popular
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:29.47,CR_DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,and have everyone go crazy for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:35.89,CR_DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,But now... it's not just for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:41.73,CR_DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,It's the four of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:54.66,Translation,Kita,0,0,0,,A sudden evening shower falls
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:00:57.62,Translation,Kita,0,0,0,,And yeah, it figures, \NI don't have an umbrella...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:01.67,Translation,Kita,0,0,0,,Who cares how the sky's feeling, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.67,0:01:04.79,Translation,Kita,0,0,0,,When it's time for the seasons to change
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:06.55,CR_DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,I never figured out what \Nit means to have "growth."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:07.55,Translation,Kita,0,0,0,,What are you supposed to wear? Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:11.51,Translation,Kita,0,0,0,,Spring and fall... yeah, where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:09.59,CR_DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,But right now, what I want
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:13.68,CR_DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,is to stay with this band and \Nhave people go crazy for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:16.51,Translation,Kita,0,0,0,,The pressure of information, suffocating
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:19.10,Translation,Kita,0,0,0,,A spiral of vertigo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:20.14,CR_DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,I want to make Nijika-chan's \Nactual dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:21.48,Translation,Kita,0,0,0,,Don't know where I am
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:27.61,Translation,Kita,0,0,0,,I can hear myself breathing \Nso loud, so loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:26.57,CR_DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,So... I can't afford to blow this audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:32.95,Translation,Kita,0,0,0,,But why? I can't hear the \Nsounds of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:31.95,CR_DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,I don't want the band to end just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.95,0:01:37.08,Translation,Kita,0,0,0,,It's not enough, not enough, \NNo one knows I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:42.25,Translation,Kita,0,0,0,,I screamed when I couldn't \Nmake a scribble of a sound
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:47.13,Translation,Kita,0,0,0,,Who am I supposed to show "just who I am" to?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:51.97,Translation,Kita,0,0,0,,So I'm singing just like the fool I am
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:55.26,Translation,Kita,0,0,0,,Let's lay it all out to the stars!
